These are bash scipts made to manager LXC containers.

The idea is to easily make a container spawn, which can access the internet, and allow you to connect with ssh.

LXC containers are used as Virtual Machines because they can be spawned fast, boot fast, and use a small amount of resources.

This is useful for testing new apps and services, or to compile a software without polluating your own computer.


